title: Afrojack - Jacked 045 2013-11-11 (Split)
description:
Hey guys,

This is Afrojack's JACKED Podcast Week 45 with split tracks. You can get this for free from the iTunes store in Podcasts, however it will not have split tracks.

For I and everyone else's conquest for knowledge on new music, uh... well what I meant to say is that this should be under fair use.

Really liking the songs in this episode.

Please help me seed if you have a service provider that does not count uploads. I have a computer rigged as a dedicated server and hopefully later I can have one in a different network setup but I don't want to get money involved in this at all so seedboxes are out of the question.

Thanks to 1001tracklists.com for the tracklist, and Afrojack for a very good episode this week!

enjoy

~impetuousbrahh
